Mouthfeel: Light to medium bodied, good carbonation, dry, and acidic. Sour is the operative word for sure.
Overall: An interesting beer, but a touch too sour. There are some nice flavors going on there, but the sour aspect overwhelms everything else. 1,134 charactersBuckyFresh, Nov 06, 2011
