4.6/5  rDev +3.8%look: 4.5 | smell: 4.5 | taste: 4.5 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 5I have been waiting to try this beer for longer than any other and I finally got my hands on it! I purchased it for 40 bucks at Downtown Wines in Somerville Massachussetts. 
